---
title: Feta-Stuffed Meatballs with Dilly Orzo and Spinach
description: We've transformed the delicious flavours of spanakopita into a weeknight orzo bowl!  Each meatball will delight your tastebuds with a bite of melty, briny feta!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/feta-stuffed-meatballs-8608e2f0.jpg
